{"tid":1463341,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「阻你飛」邊個諗出黎架？？？咁On9既。","createTime":"2019-08-13T12:47:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T12:51:27.000Z","uid":112551,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8d7ecaf2db30df45f86a79f049fd094e84e55ff1","tid":1463341,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:47:24.000Z","msg":"我覺得的確外國人點睇唔太重要，但本地點睇就好重要，<br />\n仲有人話想下星期日搞咩民陣100萬人集會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，你想消耗民意去搞個100萬人集會？點解又取消地鐵不合作運動？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想講，下星期日先係重頭戲，大家不如和理非而唔好阻人飛，唔一定要阻人飛搞個新聞先引到人關注。<br />\n<br />\n講完，鬼先會做呢啲野，打爛的士對途人施暴呢啲野本來就唔係大家原本想做既事，大家針對的既警察同政府，而非針對市民。<br />\n<br />\n政府只會幾阻你飛當民意牌去打，對政府沒傷害。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌我都咁話，6月至今開咁多支持大家既Post都係唔想搞禍件事。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">8月18日 集氣百萬人上街！</span></span>"},{"pid":"87e07e8742ff4ac31a2087ef8e447bc109a45f5b","tid":1463341,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:48:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b38ce87eef72bb9a06a0a083e75c437d88989228","tid":1463341,"uid":162272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:49:14.000Z","msg":"唉 豬隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64de750bd14d5fdb13250c1d640a2d21c142276c","tid":1463341,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:49:15.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"d275425d9bb8a651398ed5b78297fb3141cd7ee5","tid":1463341,"uid":31166,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:49:44.000Z","msg":"咁你出嚟機場叫我地散囉"},{"pid":"de95236e43e319b3552591e559bbfdfee7153dbf","tid":1463341,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d27